{"tid":1911442,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何Wayne （何蛇）算唔算第一代撚狗師","createTime":"2020-03-05T10:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T02:06:06.000Z","uid":234509,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9dcc9a82649e2bc4e636f35a620fe620691ec5b","tid":1911442,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"何冠寰離開寰宇娛樂後，他自資以十萬港元預算，在16天內拍攝了電影《生前必做七件事》[2]。為了宣傳電影，他在YouTube上傳了女主角許芯悅求救的影片，引發網民擔心許芯悅的安危而報警。後來何冠寰揭露影片只是電影預告片之後，有受騙的網民表示會杯葛電影，而他亦因涉嫌浪費警力被捕，最終未獲起訴。《生前必做七件事》一片其後獲得2014年獨立電影節最佳恐怖片獎，其預告片亦獲2014年獨立電影聚會國際電影節榮譽優異獎。何冠寰在拍罷《生前必做七件事》之後離開了電影界[1]。[3]<br />\n<br />\n何蛇行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好笑係有人話佢藍<br />\n佢屌林鄭撐醫護撐封關有罷工都藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHaters always gonna hate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6677ee224f1e99a28981699535a2c8ef2fd97871","tid":1911442,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"何蛇不嬲勁"},{"pid":"0c12d9af2fcc6b5dc01f3337947c2ab9d6c3d533","tid":1911442,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"乜香港有人黃嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺藍店返工=喺黨鐵返工=公墓園=狗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910036\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1910036</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f78c8abab9a5fa1aaa9dfd33b5e83165f9599d7","tid":1911442,"uid":77092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:04:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49d69a76db444061f7d6ceadc559b44523b1a83e","tid":1911442,"uid":234509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"scor